data.description: Come check out this 3 bedroom 2 full bath 1 car single story home! This home has a fully remodeled kitchen with granite countertops, beautiful backsplash, and customs stove hood. Tile throughout with carpet in living room and all bedrooms. Fully fenced in large backyard with desert landscaping for easy upkeep.
